Title: Excavation: Riverbed
Description:
There's a Riverbed near Maruukai in Ohn'ahran Plains that's teeming with local lore about a lost caravan!

Meet me there as quick as you can! And wear your best, old, mud-ready boots!
ObjectivesText: Meet Roska Rocktooth at the Riverbed dig site in Ohn'ahran Plains.
